works.description: Amalgam Fine Model Cars has given us a range of intricately detailed 1:8 scale replicas of some of the most desirable cars in the world, and this scale model of the highly desirable Ferrari 250 California Spyder SWB of 1960 is no exception. Available from the Ferrari Store for a cool $6,555, the incredibly detailed model is about 24 inches long, and it took a team of highly skilled model makers around 4,000 hours of work to design and create. Each individual model further took around 350 hours more to finish and build.
